#

Wagyu Beef Burger with Truffle Aioli

$25
800 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

EggGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

GourmetBeefBurgerTruffleSweet Potato

Description

Indulge in a succulent Wagyu beef burger, topped with luxurious truffle aioli, served alongside crispy sweet potato fries and a fresh arugula salad.

Ingredients

  • Wagyu beef patty: 8 oz
  • Burger bun: 1
  • Truffle oil: 1 tbsp
  • Mayonnaise: 2 tbsp
  • Sweet potatoes: 2 large
  • Arugula: 2 cups
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Paprika: 1 tsp
